            "title": "",
            "text": "<h3 class=\"inline-richtext\">Purify with<br>BIRETIX Cleanser</h3>\n<p>Cleansing is an essential first step in any acne-prone skincare regime. BIRETIX Cleanser helps remove excess oil, impurities and daily build-up without disrupting the skin barrier, leaving skin feeling balanced, refreshed and prepared for the next steps in your skincare regime. </p>",
