            "title": "",
            "text": "<h3 class=\"inline-richtext\">Treat with<br>BIRETIX Tri-Active Gel</h3>\n<p>BIRETIX Tri-Active is a targeted treatment serum clinically proven to reduce blackheads by 61% and blemishes by 76% in just 28 days*, while helping to control oil and sebum production.  </p>",
