            "title": "",
            "text": "<h3 class=\"inline-richtext\">Care with<br>BIRETIX Hydramat Fluid</h3>\n<p>Hydration and barrier support are essential for adolescent/persistent acne-prone skin. BIRETIX Hydramat helps balance excess oil while delivering lightweight hydration to support skin comfort, sensitivity and overall skin health. </p>",
