        "column_JcCKQT": {
          "type": "column",
          "settings": {
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/acnimat.jpg",
            "title": "",
            "text": "<h3 class=\"inline-richtext\">Protect with<br>HELIOCARE 360° Acnimat</h3>\n<p>No acne-prone skincare regime is complete without daily sun protection. HELIOCARE 360° Acnimat provides very high-level full-spectrum defence against UVA, UVB, visible light and infrared-A, while helping to control shine with a mattifying finish ideal for oily and blemish-prone skin.</p>",
